LOCUS       BC2_tag                   12 aa            linear   UNK 01-JAN-1980
DEFINITION  BC2_tag — a 12-aa linear epitope tag (PDRKAAVSHWQQ) from the
            N-terminal region of human beta-catenin, bound by the BC2 nanobody
            (Kd ~1.4 nM) for protein purification, immunodetection, and
            super-resolution imaging..
